Relationship Manager Retail Banking Wealth Management - HSBC Indonesia
Relationship Manager Retail Banking Wealth Management  -
Relationship Manager Retail Banking Wealth Management
Responsibilities
Responsibilities:In this role, responsible to establish and grow valuable long term relationship with HSBC Premier customers and to maximize business opportunities from other customer segments in order to contribute to growing consumer banking businessRequirements:To be successful in the role, you should meet the following requirements: Hold a minimum of Bachelor DegreeHas 2-5 years working experience in Retail Banking sales or Relationship ManagementExperience of working with high net worth individuals with proven ability to achieve sales targetsHold investment and insurance accreditation, such as Waperd and AAJIStrong knowledge on Wealth Management, financial markets and investment productsProficiency in English and Computer Literate (MS Office)Conversant in Mandarin is an additional valueHave excellent communication and presentation skills as well as strong passion in selling activitiesIs customer service oriented, has commercial acumen, has good interpersonal skill and a team playerDemonstrate a high degree of credibility and integrity If you meet the above requirements and seek a rewarding career and the opportunity to develop with a progressive international bank, please send your detailed CV (in English) to address below: HSBC - Human Resources Department address: World Trade Center, 4th Floor,Jl. Jendral Sudirman Kav.29-31, Jakarta 12920email: human-resources@hsbc.co.id To find out more information about the programme and the selection process,please visit our career site at www.hsbc.co.id/careers
